articles.author: Josh Dinner
articles.title: 'We have doubled the number of nationalities aboard' ISS as all-European SpaceX Ax-3 astronauts dock at space station - Space.com
articles.description: The Ax-3 astronauts will spend two weeks conducting science aboard the ISS before returning to Earth on a SpaceX Dragon.
